# Raw and processed data (regenerated by running the notebooks — see DATA_SOURCES.md)
# **/data/**/*.ext matches files at any depth under a data/ folder (including directly
# inside it), so both flat layouts (e.g. Switzerland) and nested raw/processed layouts
# are covered, along with any subfolder structure future countries might use.
**/data/raw/
**/data/processed/

# Large or generated data files inside any data folder
**/data/**/*.zip
**/data/**/*.csv
**/data/**/*.gtfs
**/data/**/*.gz
**/data/**/*.xml
**/data/**/*.txt
**/data/**/*.log

# OS / editor junk
.DS_Store
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
